{"word":"ταράσσω","slug":"ταράσσω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ταράσσω</el></b> [<el>ϑράσσω</el> ‘disturb, mar’] ‘cause to be in a disturbed state’, <b>agitate<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of thing, make water turbulent <b><a href='B:500 5:3'>J 5:3</a> [4] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>, 7.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ref.\">ref.</a> to mental or spiritual disturbance<b><p class=\"pp4\"/>—<pp>α.</pp></b> with <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ acc.\">acc.</a> <b><a href='B:500 11:33'>J 11:33</a>; <a href='B:510 15:24'>Ac 15:24</a>; <a href='B:510 17:8'>17:8</a>, <a href='B:510 17:13'>13</a>; <a href='B:550 1:7'>Gal 1:7</a>; <a href='B:550 5:10'>5:10</a>.<p class=\"pp4\"/>—<pp>β.</pp></b> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> construction <b><a href='B:470 2:3'>Mt 2:3</a>; <a href='B:470 14:26'>14:26</a>; <a href='B:480 6:50'>Mk 6:50</a>; <a href='B:490 1:12'>Lk 1:12</a>; <a href='B:490 24:38'>24:38</a>; <a href='B:500 12:27'>J 12:27</a>; <a href='B:500 13:21'>13:21</a>; <a href='B:500 14:1'>14:1</a>, <a href='B:500 14:27'>27</a>; <a href='B:670 3:14'>1 Pt 3:14</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ταπείνωσις\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ταραχή\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}